# .cursorrules — aiframework
# Stack: bash / none
# Generated by aiframework. Run `aiframework refresh` to update.

## Commands

- Test: `make test`
- Lint: `find . -name '*.sh' -not -path '*/.git/*' -not -path '*/vault/*' | xargs shellcheck`
- Type check: `find . -name '*.sh' -not -path '*/.git/*' -not -path '*/vault/*' | xargs bash -n`

## Conventions

- All scripts must pass shellcheck with zero warnings
- All scripts must start with set -euo pipefail for strict error handling
- All user-supplied variables must be quoted — no unquoted $VAR expansions
- NEVER use `|| true` to silence errors without understanding the failure
- NEVER use `set +e` to disable error handling without re-enabling it
- Never commit secrets or credentials — use environment variables
- Run lint + test before committing

## Key Locations

- Source: `bin/`
- Source: `docs/`
- Source: `lib/`
- Source: `templates/`
- Source: `tests/`

